leonard goodings remodeling project 
turned into a major restoration effort when he removed some siding 
and discovered his old house was actually a log cabin 
i was going to tear the siding off it and rent it out 
gooding said friday in a telephone interview i eliminated all 
the siding and came up with a log cabin its in perfect shape 
