argue that reagans military buildup and strategic defense 
initiative have brought the soviets back to the bargaining table and 
dissuaded the ussr from advancing in the third world 
but bushs ties to reagan also leave him in a relatively weak 
position to exploit the electorates frustration over trade the 
international drug trade the us decline overseas and the 
allies perceived failure to contribute fairly to the common 
defense it said 
