cathedrals in the nations oldest monastery will be 
returned to the russian orthodox church next week after 27 years of 
state ownership symbolizing progress in religious freedom 
officials announced saturday 
parts of the monastery of the caves have become museums and will 
remain in government hands the monastery was established in 1050 on 
